Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在我还小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}脑海中就常浮现出“影像”来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是在何处都感觉似曾相识的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有好几次都是有着水的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是梦中的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可我并不曾去过那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}据说是因为受到了因克拉布的反菲米娜斯的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其实真正原因是什么 我并不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是我曾想寻找些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 我踏上了旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紧急情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}受到碎石带的撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5因为是边境就没有清理者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜托了 理音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}控制船体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}保持船体平衡后立刻进行短距离跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜托了 带我到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还差… 一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在预计降落地点有生命反应？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一定在追寻那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…柑菜酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 姐姐我做了个怪梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}居然梦到小海他在光芒之中和一个裸女抱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了 看起来很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不不 应该说是很美的一个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了 刚好就像那边那个女孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能说明一下那究竟是怎么回事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我先说在前头 希望你们别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哪门子误会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你现在心里想的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总之 她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月一夏学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是那位今天转学到我们学校三年级的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是叫贵月一夏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}初次见面 我是小海的姐姐七海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}确实是“打扰”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后 明明今天在刚认识的学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么会在海的家里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}事实上由于库安连环的故障
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}造成奥尔他雷特出现严重的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}并且因克拉布也有严重的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太复杂了姐姐我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}简单来说 就是因为一些事情 没有住的地方了 并且也没带钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回家的时候偶然碰上学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}听说了她的困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就想姑且让她暂住一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为不能放着她不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么能让女孩子一个人在野外露宿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}提问 为什么在玄关那里抱在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才不知道这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学他的奥尔他雷特…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 是因为他好像不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就在照顾他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我那时候好像确实不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昏过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小海 你生病了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不知道 现在没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}照顾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是照顾吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在身边照料又抱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是如同字面上的照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}（日语照顾写作介抱）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是抱一抱病就能好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在我的星球就是这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的星球？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…是说我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月同学是来自哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}布雷尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 是来自北边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是北海道那边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…还要更远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是在留学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 从那么远的地方一个人来留学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月同学真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}日语也说得这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然不太明白 大概还是理解了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过如果有事联系老家的父母不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…这…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…有什么难言之隐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐我大概明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}超能力！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 一夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉啊 让你想起伤心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我和海人也失去了双亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以一夏酱的感受我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏酱的感受…我是非常明白啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…七海姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦 总之就是刚才说的那些原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姑且让学姐住一晚上 可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别说一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住这不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你想 我明天开始就要出远差了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本来就想着要有谁来照顾小海来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}同一个学校的人也比较放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又是女孩子还能做做饭 洗洗衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}同龄男女居然同住一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}困难时就该互相帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且小海是个温柔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不管是和多漂亮的学姐住一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不会做那种奇怪的事 这种奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有那种奇怪的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不会做的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}当…当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 刚才结巴了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你还想了想是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才没想啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这眼神明摆着在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我这眼神是什么眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这种就是那种！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小女未经世事 还请多多关照 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫我姐就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像…媳妇进门一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我送谷川回家去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好像…生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个啊…谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}关于学姐这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}助人为乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是帮助了遇上麻烦的学姐而已是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是啊…仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}送到这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天…见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 那个美女学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}居然寄住在雾岛同学家里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是怎么回事啊 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像不知不觉就变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过雾岛同学家里还有家人一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他姐姐明天开始要出远差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂喂 真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剧情急转直下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}该怎么办啊 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这下就定了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}定了…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天碰头的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那个姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她说要打包行李 就先回房了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}义大利面和味噌汤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}标准搭配吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搭配之外的标准搭配吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我搞错什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没有…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没…没事吧？不好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…与其说是不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这味道酸酸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是…冷面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想着你今天累坏了还是吃点凉的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊不 因为尝到了意想不到的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微有点吃惊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我继续吃了哦 这份冷义大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我能问你个问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐你为什么来这里留学的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为有想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哪里呢 是这附近吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不如让我带你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个啊…我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有树有池塘…是个没什么特别之处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那该怎样找呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也对呢 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就是想去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真繁忙的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天碰头会会遇到大家呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}该怎么说明呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说 这究竟是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这么说来 刚刚也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是抱一抱病就能好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拥…抱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀哎呀 这可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得赶快进行治疗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}痛痛 痛痛 都飞走哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}骗你的 这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看来修不好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 库安连环的状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全出BUG了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我从没有后悔过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}既然都到了这星球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知是不是因为太累
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一躺下 很快就入睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}连梦也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学 海人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快起来 海人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐她就要出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已经这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这件衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从姐姐那里借过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这边的睡衣…真有点让人害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对对对对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小海 姐姐我就走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你再不来送行我就哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}马…马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 小心身体 别乱花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还要好好学习 跟朋友们好好相处 别熬夜 可能会寂寞 但还是要保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏酱 小海就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我说 火车进站了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}终于走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 你寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也许…有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去之前想绕去个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想去的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐拜托的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被姐姐她？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没有自己的衣服到总是不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然有些地方有点怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}确实是个可爱的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要有了这些就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你 我今天很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然购物就是女生最爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也得和姐姐道声谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等她打电话过来的时候说就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等得都不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哟 欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是说好了要开电影制作的誓师大会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉了 我们擅自就选了你家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 这么快就亲亲密密去购物了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再说你们究竟是怎么进来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我建议你还是换一把更牢固的锁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别随便就开人家门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这完全就是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀 因为必须要好好调查嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我挚友寄宿的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你为什么会知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}趁所有人都在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}由雄心勃勃的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就雾岛海人的处女作的内容进行讨论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}既然开始了就快说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来 导演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说 为什么由她来主持啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什么啦 又是高年级的学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么 究竟要拍怎样的电影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就把我写的这本剧本拍成电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顺便说一下 这是我构思二十年 写了五年…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什么样的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是讲二十三世纪 机动兵器活跃于世界各地的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就连好莱坞也要吓得屁滚尿流的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一代商业大作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全都用CG来做你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或许不需要摄影机也有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还是拍些简单点更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就校园之类的怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学校的批准姑且还是能批下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}确实是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剧情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样的又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学校里突然出现丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}侥幸生还的主人公们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏学姐不提提意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这家伙胆子不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是主演嘛 说说你的意见嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然不是说故事方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我想看些美丽的风景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才来这里没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想去很多很多的地方 见识各种各样的新鲜事物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为有我有想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思 说得太抽象了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到处逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正就快到暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:16:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}玩乐与拍电影 一石二鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我觉得最后肯定都变成玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就那样也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不是一定就要拍一部电影出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到处去转转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或许能找到你想要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}电影的内容迟点再想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家先一起为预祝电影拍摄成功而干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这饮料是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是奇怪的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过有点甜甜的 还是挺好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我还要一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我带了很多来 喜欢喝就尽情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}炸弹！牌也出完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐 柠檬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个饮料叫什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}“活力”饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来如此啊 真让人上瘾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈哈哈…活力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总感觉有点儿晕晕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}晕晕的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 身体有点儿热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身体发热吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可真不妙呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂！两个独处的人在干什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到这边来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎么了啊 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚才你肯定觉得我妨碍你们了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是不是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那学姐觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没这么想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要在这寄住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有两个人在一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}马上就快到暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}两个人一整天都独处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}独处！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我就开门见山的问了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐你觉得海人怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？这…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海…海人同学在我困难的时候帮了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是指这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是问你觉得他怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个是什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}生体…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是我的宠物…叫理音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟然会有这样动物  我肯定晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样也挺可爱的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且还在跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正好在兴头上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来玩我特制的国王游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喔！听起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}国王游戏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}玩一下就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谁是国王！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那先来一个程度轻点儿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}3号 弹1号的脑门 下手重一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}4号 打1号耳光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你这笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么总是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}5号 和4号亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}3号 脱裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 不要给我们看你的内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}4号 做个诱惑的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}2号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和1号…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}H
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家这样很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感觉能拍成很棒的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…嗯…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那饮料是怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然…头…好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微…把眼睛闭一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:18.96,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:21.61,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:24.21,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:32.91,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋…小海…这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:36.57,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才是个笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:39.88,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:43.56,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:44.87,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.97,0:22:47.60,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:51.18,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以说出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:53.84,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:56.23,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜 雾岛同学今天请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行！一定要去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是最优先事项！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…你说了这句不能说的台词…
